{"pageProps":{"problem":{"id":"t16-train-1","grade":"7","semester":"up","category":"代数式","title":"针对训练1：用字母表示面积","difficulty":2,"tags":["代数式","面积"],"content":"如图，空白部分的面积表示错误的为（ ）\n\nA. $2x$\nB. $x(x+2)-x^2$\nC. $2(x+3)-6$\nD. $(x+3)(x+2)-x^2$","steps":[{"title":"分析各选项","content":"设矩形的长为 $x+3$，宽为 $x+2$，内部小正方形边长为 $x$\n\n空白部分面积 $= (x+3)(x+2) - x^2$\n\n展开：$= x^2 + 5x + 6 - x^2 = 5x + 6$","formula":""},{"title":"验证各选项","content":"A. $2x$ ≠ $5x + 6$，错误\nB. $x(x+2)-x^2 = x^2 + 2x - x^2 = 2x$ ≠ $5x + 6$\nC. $2(x+3)-6 = 2x + 6 - 6 = 2x$ ≠ $5x + 6$\nD. $(x+3)(x+2)-x^2 = 5x + 6$，正确","formula":"\\text{答案：A、B、C}"}]},"id":"t16-train-1"},"__N_SSG":true}